               <msContents>
                  <summary>F. i r: pen trial. F. i v and xiv r: Calendar of the Feast Days of the Apostles. Ff. ii r-iii v: Image of the Paraclete, incomplete and folios in disorder. F. iii v mentions ገብረ መድኅን and ገብረ ሥላሴ. F. iv rv: unidentified text, written in a different hand. Ff. iv r-xii v: Another copy of the Image of Paracletos, incomplete at the beginning. F. xii v mentions ገብረ ሕይወት. F<locus target="#1r">fols. 1r, </locus>-46v: Acts of Abunä Aragawi, ገድለ፡ አቡነ፡ አረጋዊ፡. F<locus target="#1r">1r, </locus>-16r: Introduction. F<locus target="#16v">16v, </locus>-30v and 47r: Image of Aragawi. F<locus target="#30v">30v</locus>-46v: Prayer of the Covenant, Ṣälotä Kidan, ጸሎተ፡ ኪዳን፡. Ff. ተፈሥሔ ኦዘንስእለኪ ደኅና Rejoice O Virgin</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <textLang/>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
